# Day 30: Capstone — GWAS Analysis
# Data sources:
#   Type 2 diabetes GWAS loci from Mahajan et al. 2018 Nature Genetics
#   (DIAbetes Genetics Replication And Meta-analysis, DIAGRAM consortium)
#   50 true association loci with published odds ratios and chromosomal positions
#   Gene names, rs IDs, and effect sizes from published T2D GWAS catalog
#   499,950 null SNPs generated programmatically with uniform p-value distribution

println("Setting up Day 30: Capstone — GWAS Analysis")
mkdir("data")

# ── File 1: Study-level sample information ──
